## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the diversity of perspectives represented. The search results primarily reflect progressive Christian viewpoints, which may not encompass the full spectrum of beliefs within Christianity. Additionally, the lack of recent data from some sources may affect the relevance of the findings. Further research could include a broader range of denominational perspectives and more recent publications to provide a more comprehensive understanding.